Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:54.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111424,114052}I'm so glad it's nice weather, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:58.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114510,118014}You were looking forward\Nto this field trip very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:03.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118723,123186}Today let's forget about studying\Nand just have fun, Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123186,125897}You're always forgetting\Nabout schoolwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:09.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125897,129150}Why don't you make a wish\Nat the Tree of Happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:13.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129150,133696}Like, "Please make me\Na little bit smart!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:15.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133946,135114}It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136532,137909}All the girls are there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:20.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138826,140912}What's the Tree of Happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141329,143122}What?\NDon't you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143122,146125}It's a tree in this park\Nwhich is popular right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:27.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146125,147251}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147251,149045}Yeah! Let's go see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159097,160598}This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:44.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160598,164894}There's a rumor that if you carve\Nyour wish on the tree, it will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164894,167814}You can carve your name\Nalong with the one you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173986,175571}There are a lot of scars…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:58.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175822,178324}Yeah… I feel sorry for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.79,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:184789,187792}Get Back the Tree of Happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188751,190294}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191003,192797}They seem in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193381,195049}What? What? What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195425,197802}Oh, Meimi. It's about\Nthe Tree of Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198094,199178}The Tree of Happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:25.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199178,205768}Yes! Hanako of Class C carved in the tree\Nand wished for a date with a boy she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205768,207520}– Then…\N– Then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207520,209647}Then it came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209647,211023}Wow! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:32.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211482,212567}I envy her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212567,215486}I'm going to go there again\Nand make more and more wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215486,217780}You have too many wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:38.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217780,218948}That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:42.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219282,222285}I asked about Kosuke,\NKazuhiko, and Akio…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222285,223953}How about Yasuhiro and Isshin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223953,226789}Well… Meimi,\Ndid you make a wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:50.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226789,230918}No, I didn't because\NI felt sorry for the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231252,233296}Meimi, you worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233296,236632}Don't think too much about\Nsuch things and just enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:04:01.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236632,241137}I thought you had made\Na wish about Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:04.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241471,244348}Don't be stupid! Why would\NI want to wish about him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244348,246225}What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246225,248853}You talked mean about me as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248853,250855}No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:14.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251314,254525}Didn't you make a wish at\Nthe Tree of Happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254525,257069}that you could catch St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257528,260907}Stupid! I don't have\Nto ask God about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260907,263034}I'll catch her by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263493,266454}That's why he can't catch her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266454,268498}– That's right!\N– You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:37.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276422,277840}Arborist?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:43.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278132,283805}Yes. I treat the trees which are\Ndamaged by disease and pollution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284138,286057}You mean a tree doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:46.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286057,286891}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:52.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287725,292563}About a year ago, in the grove on the hill\Nnear Tachibana Nature Park
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:56.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292563,296901}I found a white tree which\Nwas dying from disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:04.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301239,304659}The disease had progressed badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:08.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304659,308746}If nothing was done, it appeared\Nthat it would fall any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320967,323219}Good… It still has a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:04.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359839,364135}It took time,\Nbut the tree fully recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:10.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365928,370266}Your thoughts must\Nhave reached the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:13.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370266,373352}After that, I went there\Nto check on it from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373352,375730}But when I went there today,\Nthe tree was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376397,377982}The tree was gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378274,379442}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:24.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379442,384822}The owner of Tachibana Nature Park\Ntook it out by the roots, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385990,387909}Oh, that tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387909,391329}I want it to become the new\NTree of Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392371,393831}A new Tree of Happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:38.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394248,398210}The current tree has so many scars\Nthat we can't use it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398210,400296}We were looking for a new tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400838,402590}I beg you, Mr. Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402590,404467}Please don't continue with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:45.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404467,405760}Trees are living, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406177,407553}You're hurting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407553,410723}It's none of your business\Nwhat I do in my park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411223,414685}Or are the trees saying\Nthey're hurting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414685,417855}Yes, they are!\NYou just can't hear them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418230,419982}That's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:04.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420399,424028}The Tree of Happiness\Nis a money tree for this park.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424028,427823}Some come just to carve\Ntheir wishes on the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:11.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428491,431702}So I have no intention of stopping,\Nno matter what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:19.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435748,439001}It's best for trees to be\Nin their natural state.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439001,442338}But he's moving them\Nand carving them up…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442338,443756}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444173,447551}I'm sure your prayers\Nhave reached God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450638,452807}That's what the owner\Nof the park said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:38.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452807,458187}Yes. According to Kudo, the tree will be\Nplanted in the park tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458729,459689}Tomorrow night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460356,461190}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461190,463651}So it's in time for the opening\Nthe day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464068,466654}Then what will happen\Nto the current tree in the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:50.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467029,470449}It's terrible,\Nbut it will be disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470449,471659}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471659,474453}It'll be replaced because\Nit isn't useful anymore…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474453,477206}Trees are not an instrument\Nfor humans to make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:00.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477206,480626}So, Meimi, I would like you\Nto steal the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481335,482837}All right, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482837,484588}Count on St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487383,488676}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488676,490094}Welcome back, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494432,496142}Whose voice is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496142,498310}Meimi! It's me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501897,504608}Ruby!? You can…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506777,508571}Meimi, I'm Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509280,511824}Dad! What's that?!\NInteresting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512533,514285}It's a voice changer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514285,516245}I found it at a toy store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516245,518497}I thought I might use it for my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:46.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520541,526839}Meimi, your eyes are like stars\Nof the first magnitude in the night sky…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528507,529633}Oh, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:53.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529633,533054}The park you went to on your field trip\Nthe other day was showcased on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:09:03.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536515,543981}{\i1}As you can see nature remains undisturbed\Nhere and visitors can observe rare plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:10.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544231,550446}{\i1}Also, there are athletic and cycling courses\Nand people of all ages can find enjoyment here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550905,553824}{\i1}This is the owner\Nof the park, Mr. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554658,556911}{\i1}Hello. I'm the owner, Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:24.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558412,564752}{\i1}Over here, the Tree of Happiness is very popular\Nbecause it can make wishes come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:32.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564752,572051}{\i1}I hope you can come to Tachibana Nature Park\Nand carve your wishes in the Tree of Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572384,575846}{\i1}He is advertising\Nthe Tree of Happiness like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:40.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577056,580142}But that park has changed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580142,583479}Yes. It used\Nto be a small park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583479,585731}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:49.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585731,589068}Now we have to pay\Nan expensive entrance fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:53.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589944,593239}We often went there on dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:57.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593906,597034}It's no longer\Nthe park of our memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597910,601997}But you haven't changed since that time\Nand you're just as close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602665,604625}Of course, Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604625,605960}And will be forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609088,610131}Oh, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:14.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610131,614802}I guess we'll leave these young ones alone\Nand we'll get going. Right, Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617721,618931}You're still here, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:23.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622560,623769}I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:33.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632736,633904}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633904,635197}Is it a delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638492,639827}What the…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:49.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649003,649753}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:55.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651005,655467}"Tonight I'm going to Tachibana Nature Park\Nto get the Tree of Happiness. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655885,658095}It's a warning note from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658095,659972}There's no time to lose!
Comment: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:06.68,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:666687,666687}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:11.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:671692,671692}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:20.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676780,680910}{\i1}I'm going to ask Mr. Tachibana\Nto stop once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686248,687541}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690669,693297}That's strange.\NI wonder if anyone is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697801,699470}We've got it at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:41.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699470,701513}We had a tough time getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:47.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701889,707228}Let the rich guy know that\Nwe've got the flower he asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710564,711690}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735589,737091}It's a…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737841,740761}This flower is designated\Na national treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:25.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741679,745057}And so is this flower here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746809,748310}I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:31.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748310,751522}All of these are plants\Nthat are nearly extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752314,754525}Why are these here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:51.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768706,771542}This guy again!\NWhat a persistent fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771542,774753}He's seen too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775254,777131}What should we do with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777131,778799}He saw the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778799,782970}If he tells anyone we're selling\Nthe national treasure plants…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782970,784513}He can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784513,787725}Now that he knows our secret,\Nwe can't let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:11.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788767,791520}I'm going to the Tree of Happiness\Nto watch its replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791520,793939}Make sure you watch him\Nuntil I come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793939,795691}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799778,803657}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808412,809663}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811832,813334}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815002,817796}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830893,832644}Be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832853,833812}Count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833812,835898}Nothing is\Nimpossible for St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:01.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838192,841779}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845199,846700}You're Mr. Tachibana,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:13.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849620,853082}Oh, welcome.\NI was waiting for you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853457,854500}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:20.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854500,860798}Anyway, the Tree of Happiness that St. Tail\Nis targeting was planted around here, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861048,863425}Oh, you mean the old tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863425,865761}It's over there lying on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867221,868764}Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:32.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868764,872101}It has too many scars to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:35.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872101,875437}So we're replacing it\Nwith that new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:40.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877439,880317}Oh, then you're returning the old tree\Nto its natural habitat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880317,882611}No way we're going to do\Nsomething so time-consuming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:45.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882611,885406}We'll cut it up and make\Nbenches or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887241,888867}{\i1}What is he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888867,891412}{\i1}Is this something the owner\Nof a nature park would do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:02.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897501,902131}St. Tail hasn't shown up, has she?\NI wonder if she gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:06.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902131,906802}No. She'll definitely come\Nsince she sent the warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907261,908470}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908971,910347}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:16.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912850,916311}Okay. The transplant\Nis almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:20.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916311,920315}Well, St. Tail didn't show up.\NWhat a pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:25.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921567,925279}{\i1}What happened?!\NWhy didn't you show up, St. Tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:34.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929658,934371}From now on, I want this new\NTree of Happiness to make a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934371,937374}To commemorate this event,\NI should carve the first wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938125,939251}Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939251,941920}I wish that this park\Nbecomes more prosperous…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947759,949094}What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949094,950012}Whose voice is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950304,952514}What's that voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:57.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954641,957728}Ouch! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:00.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957728,960230}You hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960230,962691}I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963942,966153}It can't be true…\NThe tree talked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:12.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969573,972117}{\i1}Not yet.\NThe real show starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977164,978582}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979791,982336}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983295,984880}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992012,993222}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995349,996558}She has shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996558,998185}Come out! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001730,1003273}There she is.\NShe's up in the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:48.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007611,1008987}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:50.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008987,1010113}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010113,1012282}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016286,1017663}Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023293,1024461}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:11.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028840,1031051}I'm taking the Tree of Happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031051,1033512}I won't let you leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035681,1038475}I'm going to catch you\Ntoday for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038684,1041436}It's dangerous to run without\Nlooking where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:34.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050279,1054908}I'm going to catch you\Nnext time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:50.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068714,1070382}Mr. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073969,1076805}Mr. Tachibana,\Nyou're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076930,1079766}What… what are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080142,1082769}Those two confessed to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:03.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082978,1083770}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086481,1088233}You…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095866,1097117}Hello, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098201,1099411}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:23.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100829,1103165}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:25.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103165,1105417}Isn't that Mr. Tachibana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:31.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105417,1111048}He was using the nature park\Nas a cover for selling rare flowers illegally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111340,1112299}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113008,1115510}He's been a suspect for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115510,1117929}We got the warrant\Nand came here, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:40.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117929,1120140}You got a big bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:43.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120140,1123935}No wonder. I thought\Nsomething was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123935,1125228}Oh, Mr. Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125729,1126813}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126813,1128982}Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128982,1130150}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:55.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130150,1135280}I came to ask Mr. Tachibana to stop\Nthe Tree of Happiness, and I was suddenly hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:59.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135280,1139076}He was locked up because\Nhe discovered their secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:02.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139076,1142663}But I'm glad that your injury isn't serious.\NWould you like us to give you a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:05.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142663,1145666}No. I want to clear my head\Nby walking home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145666,1147876}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:13.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150629,1153131}{\i1}That's what it is. St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:21.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158387,1161890}{\i1}I couldn't get the tree back after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:25.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161890,1165727}{\i1}Even though I come here,\Nthe tree won't be here…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:45.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182744,1185831}{\i1}I'm so glad… It's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196466,1198343}Did you read today's paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198343,1199344}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199344,1201596}The owner Tachibana was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:04.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201596,1204641}The City of Seika is going\Nto manage the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:09.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204808,1209896}And Kudo replanted the Tree of Happiness\Nand he's treating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:18.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214443,1218530}It is now prohibited to carve\Nin the Tree of Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:23.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219531,1223785}From now on it is a symbol\Nof the importance of natural life
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223785,1225579}and it is to be loved by people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:32.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227122,1232043}People's wishes do come true\Nwhen they put some effort into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:36.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232461,1236131}That's quite a wise saying\Ncoming from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236131,1237007}I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:40.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237007,1240510}But if I give her any praise,\Nshe gets snobby. So I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:41.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240510,1241803}What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:42.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241803,1242929}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:46.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242929,1246016}Please put a little more effort\Ninto getting better grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247225,1248977}Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253273,1255442}Such good friends…
